ients are able to resume to the day to day activities right from next day.\r\nH V DESAI eye hospital is equippd with best in diagnostics equipments like pentacamHR , corneal wavefront analyser -Keratron scout and ORK wavefront analyser\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-269 size-full\" src=\"http://local.hvd.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/download-1.png\" alt=\"PENTACAM HR\" width=\"230\" height=\"219\" /><img class=\"wpa-image-missing-alt size-full none\" src=\"http://local.hvd.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-accessibility/imgs/alt-missing.png\" alt=\"This image requires alt text, but the alt text is currently blank. Either add alt text or mark the image as decorative.\" />\r\n<h1>SCHWIND COMBI WAVEFRONT ANALYSER</h1>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-271 size-medium\" src=\"http://local.hvd.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Lasik2-300x217.jpg\" alt=\"SCHWIND COMBI WAVEFRONT ANALYSER\" width=\"300\" height=\"217\" /><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-270 size-medium\" src=\"http://local.hvd.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Lasik1-1-300x177.jpg\" alt=\"SCHWIND COMBI WAVEFRONT ANALYSER\" width=\"300\" height=\"177\" /><img class=\"wpa-image-missing-alt size-medium none\" src=\"http://local.hvd.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-accessibility/imgs/alt-missing.png\" alt=\"This image requires alt text, but the alt text is currently blank. Either add alt text or mark the image as decorative.\" /><img class=\"wpa-image-missing-alt size-medium none\" src=\"http://local.hvd.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-accessibility/imgs/alt-missing.png\" alt=\"This image requires alt text, but the alt text is currently blank. Either add alt text or mark the image as decorative.\" />\r\n\r\nH V DESAI eye hospital offers customised solutions for laser surgeries, which includes CORNEAL WAVEFRONT OPTIMISED LASIK LASER SURGERY WAVEFRONT GUIDED LASIK LASER SURGERY PHOTOTHERAPEUTIC KERATECTOMY TOPOGUIDED LASER TREATMENTS FOR KERATOCONUS Dr Mukesh Paryani, Head of Department , is an experienced LASIK surgeon trained a